tweet: Ensure you are properly disposing of ashes created by your fireplace or wood burning stove. Place ashes in a bucket made of non-flammable material, and only store that bucket on concrete or bare mineral soil. A deck can catch fire from transferred heat. #FireplaceSafetypic.twitter.com/Cwm3kW0wYS
